  "title": "Investment Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Client Advisory:</strong> Advise HNW clients on investment needs, risk tolerance, and long-term portfolio management.</li><li><strong>Portfolio Management:</strong> Design, implement, and monitor customized investment portfolios, including asset allocation and product selection.</li><li><strong>Market Research:</strong> Analyze market trends and translate Chief Investment Officer (CIO) views into actionable insights.</li><li><strong>Relationship Management:</strong> Collaborate with Relationship Managers to acquire new clients, conduct reviews, and service existing accounts.</li><li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Adhere strictly to regulatory requirements and internal company policies when recommending products. </li></ul>",
